OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 10 May to Tue 19 May
OL,6,FInitially, slowly-evolving weather
OL,7,Fpatterns are expected in the vicinity
OL,8,Fof the UK, with low pressure over
OL,9,Fnorth western Europe and high pressure
OL,10,Fbuilding to the north of the UK.
OL,11,FWhilst largely settled conditions are
OL,12,Fpossible towards the north, there are
OL,13,Flikely to be some rain or showers
OL,14,Facross portions of England and Wales,
OL,15,Fwhich could be heavy and locally
OL,16,Fthundery. However, there is a slight
OL,17,Fchance these wetter conditions could
OL,18,Fremain over the nearby Continent.
OL,19,FDeeper into next week and beyond,
OL,20,Fthere may be a tendency for more
OL,21,Fwidely unsettled conditions across the
OL,22,FUK, with some rain or showers at
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Ftimes. Whilst some occasional warm
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fdays are possible, temperatures
OL,25,Foverall are likely to be near or below
OL,26,Faverage, especially in the north, with
